text: Jacoba Langgaard (born 24 September 1988) is a Faroese football midfielder who currently plays for ÍF/Víkingur/B68 and the Faroe Islands women's national football team. == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Faroese women's footballers Category:Faroe Islands women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders
